A Biography about Me

Michael, or what he is used to be called now as Carlos, due to having classmates with the same first name as him during Junior and
Senior High School. He is a simple person that keeps an appropriate distance to everyone he knows, but has two very close friends,
both currently studying abroad. He may be a big guy and looks intimidating, but he is a gentle, weird and funny type of guy. He may
not be that close to anyone but you can also say that he is not a stranger to anyone. He also has a very wide range of hobbies, from
games, to korean and japanese dramas, J-pop and K-pop even American movies. He is a guy that can get along with surely.
